1. JOHNSTON.

ARGUMENT.

Till now, you lived without offspring, cultivating only the Muses. You are now a sire, old age tinges your locks with snow. Whence this vigour? Was any Colchian spell at work ? 'Twas my Muse that waked your impulsive energy a year ago. So your being a father is due to me.
